When you open the browser, it defaults to national data for all sectors.

Below the chart is the "Filter/Order" button that can help you customize the data. https://t.co/k5ViJ55Mfk

tweet.user.name: EIA
tweet.text:
So, if you wanted to focus on the residential or industrial sector or a specific fuel source, you can use the "Filter/Order" menu to do that. 

For this example, let's focus on all sectors and all fuel types in Ohio. https://t.co/yie1a3KLOQ
